Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
timing_librar...gma_multiplier(25.10)    timing_librar...gma_multiplier(25.10)

Name
       timing_library_setup_constraint_corner_sigma_multiplier

Syntax
       timing_library_setup_constraint_corner_sigma_multiplier <double >

       Default: 0

       Applies  user  control  multiplier to generate a constraint table using
       sigma values applied for setup arc.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

